                                        <h1 class="page-header">&#039;Roswell, New Mexico&#039;s Otherworldly Obsession with Trump and Fake News</h1>
                                                                                                                <article id="node-238364" class="node node-blog clearfix" about="/blogs/culture/lindsay-kornick/2019/02/13/roswells-otherworldly-obsession-trump-and-fake-news" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document">
    <header>
